1
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,719
This is the Pharmacist Consultant I hired.

2
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,879
Consultant?

3
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:54,040
Think a new shell makes a turtle a spirit?

4
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:56,719
Isn't he the Medicine Apprentice I fired?

5
00:01:56,719 --> 00:02:00,879
You must be the famous Li Chiyao.

6
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,840
I guess I just have a common face.

7
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:07,439
He looks like that Medicine Apprentice.

8
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,000
Ms. Ye.

9
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:16,520
Personnel is Mystic Water Hall's job.

10
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,599
Parachuting in a consultant like this

11
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:20,120
isn't in line with the rules.

12
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:25,639
Given all the money I've earned
for the Mystic Medicine Association,

13
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:28,479
even your father, Chief Pharmacist Li,
defers to me.

14
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,080
Can't I recommend a Pharmacist Consultant?

15
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:36,919
The Mystic Medicine Association
has its rules.

16
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,120
Even you

17
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:41,039
can't simply skip the personnel process.

18
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:43,919
Down the line,

19
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,159
if something goes wrong,

20
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,960
no matter how much money you've earned,

21
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,800
can it make up for the
Mystic Medicine Association losing face?

22
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,759
Wait, what does this mean?

23
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:52,919
Ms. Ye, what's going on?

24
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:55,240
Did this guy really get in
through the back door?

25
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,319
Wuming.

26
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:58,199
What's going on here?

27
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,240
From now on, call me Yang Yunfan.

28
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,080
Is Miss Lu involved in this too?

29
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:04,879
The Mystic Water Hall folks
probably are too.

30
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:06,680
It's definitely connected to the new hire.

31
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,520
I personally recommended Pharmacist Yang.

32
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,719
I vouch for his abilities.

33
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:11,879
If anything goes wrong,
I'll take responsibility.

34
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,120
Sorry,

35
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,919
how about I take him to the
Mystic Water Hall?

36
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,840
That'd be perfect.

37
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,159
No need.

38
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:26,120
I'll handle my own people.

39
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,360
Let's go.

40
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:39,199
Why is Miss Lu personally
getting into this fight?

41
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:41,120
Could she know the new consultant?

42
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:43,319
Possibly. I just saw them whispering.

43
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:44,560
What are you all muttering about?

44
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,080
Get back to work!

45
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,759
Look how hot you are.

46
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:01,439
From now on,

47
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:03,639
don't do consultations outside
in this heat.

48
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:06,000
Your health comes first.

49
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,000
Don't worry.

50
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,599
Lu Tanxiang is watching over my patients.

51
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,319
Also,

52
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:12,879
if that nitpicky little Ye Qingxue

53
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:13,560
gives you any trouble,

54
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,240
just tell me.

55
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,360
Ye Qingxue?

56
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,839
What's there to fear?

57
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,720
I've got my brother-in-law
backing me, right?

58
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,439
It's fine.

59
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,759
Son-in-law!

60
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:28,399
What brings you here?

61
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,120
Have a seat.

62
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,160
Head Pharmacist Lu,

63
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,560
you treat me like a son-in-law,

64
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,920
but Miss Lu may not want to marry me.

65
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,519
How could that be?

66
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:38,800
Sit down and tell me what's up.

67
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,480
Sit down and talk.

68
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,120
Brother-in-law,

69
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,240
how could that be, brother-in-law?

70
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,360
My sister won't say it,

71
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,519
but her heart is all yours.

72
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:46,920
She always talks about her
"brother-in-law" to me.

73
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,920
Relax, it's all good.

74
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,560
Really.

75
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,720
Pour some more water.

76
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,439
Drink some more.

77
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,879
Do you know what kind of

78
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:08,839
crappy Pharmacist Consultant

79
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,600
Ye Qingxue brought to Premier Pharmacy?

80
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,360
Some "consultant," my foot.

81
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:19,519
It's that trashy Medicine Apprentice
I kicked out of Premier Pharmacy.

82
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,759
Ye Qingxue slapped a
consultant title on him

83
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:26,120
and brazenly brought him back to me.

84
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,399
She's treating me like a fool!

85
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,319
Son-in-law, calm down.

86
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,519
Think about it.

87
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,079
No matter who he is,

88
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,879
to get into the
Mystic Medicine Association,

89
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:38,399
he has to pass through
our Mystic Water Hall, right?

90
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,199
Right.

91
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:39,519
He won't get in.

92
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,959
Don't worry.

93
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:41,360
He won't get in.

94
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:44,319
I guarantee he won't make it back.

95
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:45,560
Won't make it back!

96
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,439
He definitely won't make it back!

97
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,600
Then it's up to you all to deliver.

98
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,040
Don't worry.

99
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:54,839
The contest is about to start.

100
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:55,920
Take this, quick.

101
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,160
Head Pharmacist,

102
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,639
this...

103
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:08,199
this is the Number Zero we're looking for?

104
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,120
Are you sure?

105
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,040
I...

106
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,120
I'm not very sure either.

107
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:19,360
I saw him at the venue back then.

108
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,839
He even helped me hand out equipment.

109
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:24,040
And spooked me with a mask.

110
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:32,160
Right after Ye Qingxue started
investigating Number Zero,

111
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,959
she recruited him.

112
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,839
By your logic,

113
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,759
I also saw him at the
Mystic Medicine Tournament.

114
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,199
So that means

115
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:45,360
the Sea-Calming Mind Manual
is very likely in his hands.

116
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,480
Don't worry, brother-in-law.

117
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,519
Leave taking him down to me.

118
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:53,600
I'll force him to use
the manual in public.

119
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,519
Caught red-handed.

120
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,199
We'll take him down right there.

121
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,480
He thinks a painted-up turtle

122
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,519
can pass itself off
as the Black Tortoise.

123
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,079
He dares touch my people,

124
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,040
mess with my things,

125
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,639
I'll make him pay dearly.

126
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,199
Calm down.

127
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,560
Good son-in-law, drink some water.

128
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,720
Here, take a sip.

129
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,720
Cool down.

130
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:35,240
Finally I get to show my stuff.

131
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:38,920
Excuse me.

132
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,160
Hello, what brings you in today?

133
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:41,399
Sorry, wrong consultation room.

134
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,360
I'm better than the guy next door...

135
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,560
Hurry!

136
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,439
It's been the whole morning already.

137
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:19,079
How come there's not a single patient?

138
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,279
Hello.

139
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,680
Hello.

140
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:26,879
Hello.

141
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:28,160
Pharmacist Yang Yunfan, at your service.

142
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:29,800
Um, you know...

143
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,439
I'd like to ask where the pantry is.

144
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,039
Left down the hall, find it yourself.

145
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,159
Thanks.

146
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,080
Why?

147
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,720
This shouldn't be happening.

148
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,200
Hello, are you here for a consultation?

149
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:01,399
Young man, please change the trash bag.

150
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:08,039
Am I really here for a consultation,

151
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,519
or am I here to grow old waiting?

152
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,720
These days,

153
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,919
do people sneak in the back door
for treatment?

154
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,240
Great,

155
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,080
and it's an emergency too.

156
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,279
You treated me without permission again.

157
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:02,039
You're the one who snuck into my clinic.

158
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:03,879
Besides,

159
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,600
I just used a few needles on you

160
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,120
to perk you up.

161
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,440
What?

162
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:12,399
You think your life's too long?

163
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:14,919
Didn't you promise to cure my Gu parasite?

164
00:10:14,919 --> 00:10:15,679
Backing out now?

165
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:20,039
Could you show a bit of gratitude?

166
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,840
Just as I thought,

167
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,080
all men are the same.

168
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,519
Sweet talk on the outside,

169
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:34,480
who knows what you're really scheming.

170
00:10:37,519 --> 00:10:38,440
What are you doing?

171
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,240
The fee's paid.

172
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,799
Now get rid of the Gu parasite.

173
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,080
That's not what I meant.

174
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,480
You're a nurse now.

175
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,919
You may leave.

176
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:54,600
Through the front door.

177
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:04,759
I thought I heard something just now.

178
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,440
Nothing.

179
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,639
There are no patients,

180
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:10,679
so I'm just talking to myself.

181
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,600
No patients.

182
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,480
Not a single one.

183
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,440
It's been all morning,

184
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:19,440
not even a minor headache or fever.

185
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:23,840
I feel like a decoration.

186
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:31,120
Don't tell me you haven't registered
at Mystic Water Hall yet?

187
00:11:32,559 --> 00:11:33,360
Register?

188
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,600
Register for what?

189
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:38,440
New pharmacists must register
at Mystic Water Hall

190
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,080
and complete three onboarding steps

191
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,480
before treating any patients.

192
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,919
Without official status,

193
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,840
who'd dare seek treatment from you?

194
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,919
I had no idea!

195
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:46,919
Nobody told me!

196
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:51,000
Sorry, I forgot to mention it.

197
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,320
That scared me!

198
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,399
I thought my medical skills
weren't good enough.

199
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:00,480
Turns out it was a paperwork issue.

200
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,679
Let me take you there now.

201
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,159
Don't panic if you cough up blood.

202
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:24,200
It's just the toxins leaving.

203
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,960
I've cured your Gu parasites for good.

204
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,440
Remember to pay the fee next time!

205
00:12:47,679 --> 00:12:49,120
This place is huge!

206
00:12:53,639 --> 00:12:56,559
Hasn't the Lu family only run
Mystic Water Hall for a few years?

207
00:12:57,879 --> 00:13:01,320
Mystic Water Hall trains disciples
for the Mystic Medicine Association,

208
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,440
oversees all the pharmacies,

209
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,440
and coordinates evaluations.

210
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,360
Naturally, it can't be small.

211
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:10,279
Besides, the Yang ancestors
originally founded it.

212
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,320
After the Lu family took over,

213
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,000
we just renovated the old site.

214
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,480
I see.

215
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,879
Come on, let me show you around.

216
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,320
So, what do you think?

217
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:28,480
This atmosphere,

218
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,679
this smell...

219
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:34,080
Isn't this just a big bathhouse?

220
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,240
Medicine rises formless,

221
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,759
qi flows through nine meridians,

222
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:42,840
heavenly healing unites spirits,

223
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:45,519
returning to the formless.

224
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:49,360
You folks at Mystic Water Hall
are quite unique.

225
00:13:52,159 --> 00:13:53,039
What's wrong with you?

226
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:53,360
Me?

227
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,039
Is this Mystic Water Hall

228
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:56,159
or some kind of mental rehab center?

229
00:13:57,759 --> 00:14:00,679
Each pharmacy in our Association
uses different techniques.

230
00:14:00,679 --> 00:14:02,039
So the people who come to work here

231
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:03,840
naturally practice all kinds of techniques.

232
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,720
You'll get used to it.

233
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:08,360
That arm strength technique
is pretty powerful, huh?

234
00:14:30,679 --> 00:14:32,519
Welcome, Lu Tanxiang

235
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:34,120
ID number 25252

236
00:14:35,679 --> 00:14:37,200
Welcome, Yang Yunfan

237
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,360
ID number 8

238
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,480
Quite high-tech

239
00:14:43,039 --> 00:14:43,559
Let's go

240
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,480
Deputy Chief Song

241
00:14:54,399 --> 00:14:56,919
Bringing Premier Pharmacy's
new pharmacist in for onboarding.

242
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:00,840
Premier Pharmacy?

243
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,039
Yang Yunfan

244
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,720
Today

245
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,879
you're in luck

246
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,840
I'll personally proctor your exam

247
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,039
Hold on

248
00:15:18,039 --> 00:15:20,039
Deputy Chief Song, it's just an onboarding

249
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,279
Lu Tanxiang

250
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,360
The old man is waiting for you
in his office.

251
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,240
Get going

252
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,039
Okay

253
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:29,720
Go on

254
00:15:37,879 --> 00:15:39,879
I'll make you suffer

255
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:42,000
The nerve
